{"title":"红勤巧俭","authors":["谢觉哉"],"dates":[{"year":1960,"month":3,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"红勤巧俭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谢觉哉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——为纪念“三八”节五十周年作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要红到底，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要红得透。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"集体主义好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"个人主义臭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为公不为私，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敢想又敢做。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工作与学习，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天天忙不足。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“要赚猪儿钱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要伴猪儿眠”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小孩衣整洁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便见母亲贤。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"运用手脑并，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照顾内外兼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"况今百行业，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妇女都争先。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不向织女乞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不作无米炊。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凿开脑里窍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"运用手如飞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"着眼要远大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用心入细微。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工农商学业，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都有女权威。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不怕来的紧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只怕去的松。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"必须算细账，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才能有大丰。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗粟尺布积，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太仓广被充。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俭是治家宝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为私也为公。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}